Package: SPSScodebook
Type: Package
Title: Generate a Codebook for a SPSS dataset
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Thorsten", "Henke", email = "SPSScodebook@thorsten-henke.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: One of the compelling features of SPSS sav data format is the ability to store 
    additional information on the variables and their respective values directly in the SPSS data
    file. To have access to these information you usually need an SPSS installation, which on the 
    one hand requires a licence and on the other is an additional program the user has to open. The 
    To access these information from within  the R environment a collection of lean procedures 
    is provided that simplyfies the process of variable and value label extraction from a SPSS 
    data set. Addtionaly the procedures are written in such a way that functionality for new 
    packages can be added dynamically. 
Suggests: 
    haven
